# Minimal ORCA validation input for Fir.
# Purpose: confirm the orca/6.1.0 module chain loads and ORCA spawns its own
# MPI across the requested ranks (NOT srun/mpirun). Water B3LYP/def2-SVP single
# point, finishes in seconds.
# NOTE: keep the nprocs value below equal to the SBATCH ntasks in the job
# script. Do not write percent, bang, or star characters in these comments;
# ORCA scans for block markers even inside hash comments and will error out.
! B3LYP def2-SVP TightSCF
%pal nprocs 4 end
%maxcore 3000
* xyz 0 1
O   0.00000   0.00000   0.00000
H   0.00000   0.00000   0.95720
H   0.92660   0.00000  -0.24010
*
